<em>Enlightenment and Dissent</em>, 17: 17&ndash;47.</li>

<li>Wells, Joan, 1982. &ldquo;The Psychology of David Hartley and the
Root Metaphor of Mechanism,&rdquo; <em>Journal of Mind and
Behavior</em>, 3(3&ndash;4): 259&ndash;74.</li>

<li>Willey, Basil, 1940. <em>The Eighteenth Century Background:
Studies on the Idea of Nature in the Thought of the Period</em>,
London: Chatto and Windus, 1940.</li>

<li>Wroe, Ann, 2010. &ldquo;Shelley&rsquo;s Good Vibrations: His
Marginal Notes to Hartley&rsquo;s <em>Observations on Man</em>,&rdquo;
<em>The Wordsworth Circle</em>, 41(1): 36&ndash;41.</li>
</ul>
</div> 

